Title: Caged
Actors: Eleanor Parker, Agnes Moorehead, Ellen Corby, Hope Emerson
Plot: Frightened 19-year-old Marie Allen gets sent to an Illinois penitentiary for being an accomplice in an armed robbery. A sympathetic prison head tries to help, but her efforts are subverted by cruel matron Evelyn Harper. Marie's harsh experiences turn her from doe-eyed innocent to hard-nosed con.
Awards: Nominated for 3 Oscars. Another 1 win & 1 nomination.
